  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/54dd3da1f44b0bf7eb7fb85caa7366e7.avif?t=1773847079\" width=1280 height=1216 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/72aa5ed42fea4a20f25435530105c2a3.webp?t=1773847079\" width=339 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/d5f7c74814390740b9d4591b2dee5fb8.poster.avif?t=1773847079\" width=1170 height=457 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/d5f7c74814390740b9d4591b2dee5fb8.webm?t=1773847079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>You’ve inherited the family cleaning business, and now it’s your turn. Clean homes, workplaces, and even unusual places like space stations, preparing them for use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/4d0f044d91ffe2a70fa97003f6472dcd.webp?t=1773847079\" width=339 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/648f5a61a58a7066358f1ca3b17f3fbe.poster.avif?t=1773847079\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/648f5a61a58a7066358f1ca3b17f3fbe.webm?t=1773847079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Scrub dirt, wash away stains and restore order with sponges, vacuums, steam cleaners and the pressure washer.<br>Complete jobs to earn money and unlock new tools that strengthen your cleaning arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/1ae61ac9f8dd295f0a5d8caeff26b6ed.webp?t=1773847079\" width=339 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/75a6f47ea19f296d2fc4b810f63a9866.poster.avif?t=1773847079\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/75a6f47ea19f296d2fc4b810f63a9866.webm?t=1773847079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>No rush and no stress. It's just you, your tools and a mess waiting to be transformed into something perfect. <br>Fully enjoy the satisfying feeling of cleaning.<br>If you want a challenge, aim for the leaderboard by finishing jobs with maximum efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/6061655d737e2db4056eccdc14a4cf68.webp?t=1773847079\" width=339 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/75688c723a86e19361a0119f9fa6c074.poster.avif?t=1773847079\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/75688c723a86e19361a0119f9fa6c074.webm?t=1773847079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Each job tells its own story. Clean unique locations and experience their atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/052556a95f623dd6ecdd2b482fe5e75d.webp?t=1773847079\" width=339 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/da6b949122102e7baf7b44a97d44cd09.poster.avif?t=1773847079\" width=1170 height=457 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413190/extras/da6b949122102e7baf7b44a97d44cd09.webm?t=1773847079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Customize your gear with different gloves, trash cans and more.<br>Whether you prefer a clean and simple style or a bold and colorful look, make every job feel like your own.</p>",
